      #slider
        #viewport
          .slider-content(id='passprotect')
            p PassProtect is a cross-platform password manager app that I created when I got tired of trying to remember all my passwords and losing the sticky notes I used to write them on. I've really focused on security and UX design in this app.
            img(src='images/projects/passprotect.png')
            p
              a(href='http://passprotect.co') Visit Website
              a(href='https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id906481898') Download for iOS
              a(href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.passprotect') Download for Android
          .slider-content(id='dyli')
            .col
              img#logo(src='images/projects/dyli1.png')
              br
              p I developed the front-end of dyli, a unique fashion app that lets you discover designers, brands, and boutiques based on your fasion tastes.
              p
                a(href='https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id858505722') Download
                a(href='http://dyliapp.com') Learn More
            .col
              img(src='images/projects/dyli2.png')
          .slider-content(id="remotemusic")
            .col
              img(src='images/projects/remotemusic.png')
            .col
              h1 Remote Music
              p Remote Music is a proof of concept application that hosts a web server from an iOS device, allowing computers on the same network to connect and play songs from the device's music gallery. I decided to open source this app to demonstrate how I was able to accomplish this and allow others to learn from the source code.
              p
                a(href='https://itunes.apple.com/app/id687568996') Download for iOS
                a(href='https://github.com/gavyaggarwal/Remote-Music') View Source Code
